<div class="general-welcome-content grid">
	<section id = "categories">
		<div class="row">
			<% @categories.each do |category| %>
					<div class="columns medium-4">
						<%=  link_to category_path(category) do%><label class = "cat_title"><%= category.name %></label><% end %><br>
						<%=  link_to category_path(category) do %><%= image_tag category.thumbnail, class: "welcome_thumbnail" %><%end%>		
					</div>			
			<% end %>
		</div>
	</section>
	<section id = "services">
		<a name="services"></a>
		<h3 data-magellan-destination="services">Services</h3>
			<div class="row">
				<div class="medium-6 columns">
					<p>We don't have the technology to record or take pictures with the blinks of our eyes but the service and level of professionalism I provide is damn near close to it.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="medium-6 columns">
					<p>Services I offer include but not limited to:</p>
					<ul>
						<li>Weddings, Engagements, Bridal Showers</li>
						<li>Portraits: Family, Professional, Personal</li>
						<li>Events</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
	</section>
	<section id = "contact">
		<a name="contact"></a>
		<h3 data-magellan-destination="contact">Contact</h3>
			<div class="row">
				<address>
					<p>Phone: 713-555-5555</p>
					<p>Email: <a href="mailto:rick@rickydphotography.com"></a></p>
					<p>Stop by my office at:<p>
					<p>742 Evergreen Terrace</p>
					<p>Springfield (next to Shelbyville)</p>
				</address>
			</div>
	</section>
</div>